    "description": "Neon Puzzle Ball is a fun and challenging 2D action puzzle platformer.<br>• With simple, responsive controls, the challenge lies in figuring out which modifiers and abilities to activate to navigate each level.<br>• Use your platforming skills to find the key and unlock the door to progress.<br>• As you play, new modifiers and hazards are introduced, increasing both the fun and the challenge!<br>• Enjoy the thrill of discovering the path ahead or freely retry levels to achieve quicker times.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007260/extras/baf9eaa34eec8e7ae54a56c49d293ef3.poster.avif?t=1722930973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007260/extras/baf9eaa34eec8e7ae54a56c49d293ef3.webm?t=1722930973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007260/extras/baf9eaa34eec8e7ae54a56c49d293ef3.mp4?t=1722930973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2></strong><br>• Explore multiple gameplay modifiers such as Bounce, Timed Jump, Float, Teleport, Move, Boost, Shield, Inversion, and more.<br>• Challenge yourself against each level's 3-star completion time.<br>• Play through 64 engaging levels.<br>• Customize your Neon Puzzle Ball with various skins.<br>• No ads or in-app purchases.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007260/extras/d79ca64577cda1faca5f376f04163574.poster.avif?t=1722930973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007260/extras/d79ca64577cda1faca5f376f04163574.webm?t=1722930973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shar